                    <span class="checked-info"><i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check"></i><p>Sed lectus donec amet eu turpis interdum.</p></span>
                    <span class="checked-info"><i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check"></i><p>Nulla at consectetur vitae dignissim porttitor.</p></span>
